title: HAVING A BABY? | Robby and Penny
author: Robby and Penny
description:
So Christen was showing a lot of the familiar symptoms that come with a pregnancy. And when I confronted her about it she said that we would be having a gender reveal for our new baby?!? This was all very shocking and happening very VERY fast. This video will reveal who will be joining our family!
